        "solution": "Pagal užrašą nustatome atitiktis: $A \\leftrightarrow K, B \\leftrightarrow M, C \\leftrightarrow N$. Tada $\\angle C = \\angle N = 75^{\\circ}$. \\angle C = 75^{\\circ} Trikampio kampų suma yra $180^{\\circ}$, tad $\\angle B = 180^{\\circ} - (40^{\\circ} + 75^{\\circ}) = 65^{\\circ}$. \\angle B = 180^{\\circ} - 115^{\\circ} = 65^{\\circ}",
