          "Metodas. Pavyzdys: $\\frac{6}{\\sqrt{2}} = \\frac{6 \\cdot \\sqrt{2}}{\\sqrt{2} \\cdot \\sqrt{2}} = \\frac{6\\sqrt{2}}{2} = 3\\sqrt{2}$."
