          "$\\frac{1}{1} = 1$ $\\frac{2}{1} = 2$ $\\frac{3}{2} = 1,5$ $\\frac{5}{3} \\approx 1,667$ $\\frac{8}{5} = 1,6$ $\\frac{13}{8} = 1,625$ $\\frac{21}{13} \\approx 1,615$",
